The other half in a month?

299
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,360
Ms. Fang,

300
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:27,000
are you planning to sell all the clothes

301
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,360
and get paid

302
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,320
before paying the rest?

303
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,550
What if you

304
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:31,630
can't sell them?

305
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:33,630
To be honest,

306
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,240
Nan's relative also

307
00:12:35,550 --> 00:12:36,480
wanted to do this.

308
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,670
I didn't agree.

309
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,600
But you just said

310
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,750
this isn't a small amount.

311
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:43,510
You have to give me some time.

312
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:45,750
Okay.

313
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,440
You pay half in three days

314
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,320
and take 30% of them.

315
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,960
You pay the full amount in six days

316
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:50,720
and take them all.

317
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,000
That's the only condition.

318
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,750
Deal?

319
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:53,870
Okay.

320
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:55,670
Remove all the

321
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:56,720
tags and labels.

322
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:58,630
If I pay on time,

323
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,360
none

324
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,670
to anyone else.

325
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,030
Deal.

326
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,790
Bring 159,200 yuan

327
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:06,080
at noon in three days.

328
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:07,510
If you can't pay the rest,

329
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,240
the deposit

330
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,750
is mine.

331
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:12,790
Draft the contract.

332
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,630
You agreed?

333
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:16,870
Yes.

334
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:18,750
Ms. Zhang is right.

335
00:13:18,910 --> 00:13:20,240
Those clothes are very good.

336
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:21,630
It's a rare chance.

337
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,390
But do you have that much money?

338
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,120
Over 350,000,

339
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,480
almost 360,000!

340
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,320
Yes.

341
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:29,320
Where are you going to
find that much money?

342
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:31,750
I was impulsive at the time.

343
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,960
We'll figure something out.

344
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,240
Although it's difficult.

345
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:38,510
If you can't raise the money,

346
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,630
then it's my fault.

347
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,910
Why did I give you this terrible idea?

348
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:44,630
Ms. Zhang,

349
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:45,840
don't say that.

350
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,120
Don't call me that.

351
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:48,360
I'm not your leader anymore.

352
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,440
Wanzhi,

353
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,120
I'm sorry.

354
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:52,270
Goodbye.

355
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,630
Li!

356
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,270
Juan, get her back.

357
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,080
We're gonna need her

358
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,120
to help us sell the clothes.

359
00:13:57,320 --> 00:13:58,840
Can you get the money?

360
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,270
There are still three days.

361
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,390
I'll think of something.

362
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:02,750
Go bring her back.

363
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:03,510
- Go.
- Li!

364
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:05,000
Li!

365
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,390
Loans require collateral

366
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:14,960
and a guarantor.

367
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,550
That's a strict requirement.

368
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:17,510
Even if you have them,

369
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:18,960
three days won't be enough.

370
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,240
But I'm in a hurry.

371
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,720
Everyone who comes is in a hurry.

372
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,360
Is there any other way?

373
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,750
If there were another way,

374
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:27,150
it wouldn't be a strict requirement.

375
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:41,440
(Who is it?)

376
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,240
Hello.

377
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:44,870
This is Fang Wanzhi.

378
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:52,910
Ms. Fang.

379
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,150
Long time no see.

380
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,270
I'm so happy to see you.

381
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:57,150
Get in.

382
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:58,510
I've booked

383
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,790
a new restaurant.

384
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,750
Their food is especially delicious.

385
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,320
No, thanks.

386
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:04,960
What's up?

387
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,790
Let's talk on the bus.

388
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:07,910
Come on.

389
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:18,320
Ms. Fang,

390
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,870
have you changed your mind?

391
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,440
That's great!

392
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:25,320
I'll transfer two houses

393
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:25,840
to you first.

394
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,120
Yishan Lake

395
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,120
or Jingshan Garden?

396
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,600
Whichever you prefer.

397
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,320
You've misunderstood.

398
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:36,630
I want to start a business.

399
00:15:36,870 --> 00:15:37,550
I'm here to borrow

400
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,840
300,000 yuan from you.

401
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,030
I'll help you

402
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:43,510
after we get married.

403
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,150
No.

404
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:44,630
Of course,

405
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:45,910
we don't have to get married now.

406
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,510
As long as you're my girlfriend,

407
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,960
I'll give you the houses and the money.

408
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,150
Be my sugar daddy?

409
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,600
Do you think I'm that kind of person?

410
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:54,960
Ms. Fang.

411
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:56,200
Ms. Fang, I...

412
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:58,000
I misunderstood. Ms. Fang!

413
00:15:58,550 --> 00:15:59,720
I'm sorry.

414
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:07,320
Ms. Fang, I'm sorry.

415
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,550
Mr. Jia,

416
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,960
I just want to borrow some money.

417
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,080
I'll pay interest.

418
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:14,270
I understand.

419
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,550
My friends and driver

420
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:16,600
have told me

421
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,390
how to pursue girls.

422
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:19,200
No.

423
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,150
Wait a minute.

424
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:26,750
Here.

425
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:30,240
What's this?

426
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:31,720
Pursuing girls

427
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,080
comes at a price.

428
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:36,200
But given our current relationship,

429
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:36,600
I can't

430
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:38,150
give you 300,000 yuan

431
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,270
at once.

432
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,550
Let's take it slow.

433
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,720
Here's 20,000 yuan.

434
00:16:44,390 --> 00:16:45,600
I only have one request.

435
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,000
You must

436
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,480
give me a chance

437
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,550
to treat you to dinner later.

438
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:54,150
I've been quite busy lately.

439
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,670
Consider this 20,000 yuan

440
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,510
a loan.

441
00:16:56,670 --> 00:16:58,390
Is 10% annual interest okay?

442
00:16:58,630 --> 00:16:59,480
If you agree,

443
00:16:59,550 --> 00:17:00,550
I'll write an IOU right away.

444
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:02,240
No need, Ms. Fang.

445
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,670
That's too much trouble.

446
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:04,310
Just take it.

447
00:17:04,510 --> 00:17:05,880
Then I can't take your money.

448
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,270
Fine.

449
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:10,000
Write an IOU then.

450
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:25,680
You want to borrow money from me?

451
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,790
Let me tell you,

452
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,480
I swore an oath.

453
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,680
I'm always the one

454
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,110
borrowing money from others.

455
00:17:33,350 --> 00:17:35,030
Nobody can borrow a single

456
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:36,240
penny from me.

457
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,160
Last year,

458
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:38,310
I borrowed 200,000 yuan

459
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:39,270
from my brother.

460
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:41,270
He's been pressuring me to pay it back

461
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,000
every day.

462
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,830
It made my husband and me

463
00:17:43,830 --> 00:17:44,480
argue every day.

464
00:17:44,480 --> 00:17:45,440
He wants a divorce.

465
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:46,920
Fine, let's divorce. I'm not afraid.

466
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:47,920
I earned this money

467
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:49,960
through my own abilities.

468
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:51,510
Why should I pay him back?

469
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:52,680
Don't even think about it.

470
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,160
Ms. Fang,

471
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:00,070
what happened to you?

472
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,550
How much do you owe?

473
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:02,920
Will those debt collectors

474
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:04,790
come after me?

475
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,110
What I mean is,

476
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,920
business is tough right now.

477
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:13,480
If you can't pay the rent,

478
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:15,440
remember to tell me in advance

479
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,070
so I can find a new tenant.

480
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,510
Hey, come with me.

481
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:26,640
Where to?

482
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:27,920
To the post office.

483
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:29,200
To call my home.

484
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:29,880
Wait.

485
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,790
You can call from downstairs.

486
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,030
Are you coming or not?

487
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,160
I wanna ask my family for money.

488
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:40,400
I don't want anyone to hear.

489
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,240
Fine.

490
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:53,350
(Hello?)

491
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:55,310
Hello, this is Wanzhi.

492
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:56,720
Wanzhi?

493
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,480
What a coincidence that you're calling.

494
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,310
(I happened to be home today.)

495
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,350
(How are you?)

496
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,350
(Are you alright?)

497
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,880
Grandma Yu is worried
you're not eating well.

498
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,550
She even said she'd

499
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:08,200
send you some

500
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:09,310
preserved fish and pickles.

501
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:11,200
No need to send me food.

502
00:19:12,030 --> 00:19:13,200
Actually, I just wanted to...

503
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:14,680
(You...)

504
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,240
(What do you want?)

505
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:17,160
Hello,

506
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:18,790
Wanzhi.

507
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,680
I didn't

508
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,790
hear you clearly.

509
00:19:21,270 --> 00:19:22,350
Could you repeat it?

510
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,880
Actually, I just wanted

511
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:38,510
to wish you and Grandma Yu

512
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:41,200
good health and all the best.

513
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:43,400
You called just

514
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:44,750
to check on us?

515
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:48,790
Wanzhi,

516
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:50,880
how are you doing over there?

517
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:52,550
Is your work

518
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:53,440
going well?

519
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,400
(Have you considered)

520
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:56,310
(coming back to study?)

521
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,960
(Is there anything I can do for you?)

522
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,510
(Just tell me.)

523
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:01,070
Nothing.

524
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,160
I just miss you.

525
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,510
Say hello to Grandma Yu for me.

526
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,310
You...

527
00:20:09,310 --> 00:20:10,160
Let me talk to her.

528
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:12,960
She hung up.

529
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,680
She must be homesick,

530
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:16,590
being alone far from home.

531
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:18,160
But she's also stubborn.

532
00:20:19,310 --> 00:20:19,960
Mr. Meng,

533
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,400
could you buy me a ticket?

534
00:20:21,640 --> 00:20:22,480
I'll go to Shenzhen

535
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,030
to see if I can bring her back.

536
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:44,640
Wanzhi,

537
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,200
your dad just

538
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,350
gave you 30,000 yuan.

539
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,790
Even if it doesn't help,

540
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,960
you shouldn't feel wronged.

541
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,240
After all, not many people

542
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:54,590
can come up with that
much money at once.

543
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:58,110
I didn't ask him for the money.

544
00:20:59,030 --> 00:21:00,720
He's an honest man. He
doesn't have any money.

545
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,400
He must have been saving up

546
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:03,920
that 30,000 yuan for a long time.

547
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:07,240
We probably won't be able

548
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:09,310
to raise the first installment.

549
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,440
It's okay.

550
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,480
At worst, we'll go

551
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:15,880
to Mr. Huang and get

552
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:16,510
the deposit back.

553
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:18,240
Impossible.

554
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,240
Why?

555
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,270
We didn't take the clothes.

556
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,000
He can't just take our deposit.

557
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:24,160
That's what the contract says.

558
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:28,720
I thought things would work out.

559
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:31,240
I was too naive.

560
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,680
I wanted to succeed too much.

561
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:16,720
Juan.

562
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,510
Have some tea.

563
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,480
Even the hardest things

564
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:28,510
will pass if you just endure them.

565
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,510
Thanks.

566
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,400
What?

567
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:36,550
Why are you crying?

568
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:39,160
I'm heartbroken about your 20,000 yuan.

569
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:41,550
I'd forgotten about it.

570
00:22:42,550 --> 00:22:43,720
I asked

571
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,720
all my friends.

572
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:47,200
But they're just workers.

573
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,400
I only managed

574
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:51,030
to scrape 2,000 yuan.

575
00:22:53,590 --> 00:22:54,960
They are not easy either.

576
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:57,270
Give the money

577
00:22:57,270 --> 00:22:58,240
back to them.

578
00:22:58,830 --> 00:23:00,480
I even called Qian.

579
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,350
I wanted to borrow money from her,

580
00:23:03,510 --> 00:23:05,590
but she sounded upset,

581
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:07,070
so I didn't ask.

582
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,200
Wanzhi,

583
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,830
let's go ask Mr. Huang.

584
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,030
I can go for you.

585
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:16,920
I'll kneel and beg him.

586
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:17,550
He'll understand.

587
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:18,200
Do you think

588
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,960
that will work with someone like him?

589
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,240
Is there no other way?

590
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:24,880
Juan,

591
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,240
I've asked everyone I could.

592
00:23:30,030 --> 00:23:31,240
Besides you,

593
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:32,550
I have no other friends in Shenzhen,

594
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,400
let alone wealthy ones.

595
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:37,480
If we fail,

596
